Level 0 contains how to connect to the challege server to solve the challenge.
We use SSH to connect to the challenge server.
whatis SSH ->(SSH client) is a program for logging into a remote machine and for executing commands on a remote machine.
here our host server will be bandit.labs.overthewire.org which will listen us on port-2220
our username will be the bandit level eg for bandit 0 it will be bandit0.

how to connect to the bandit0 server ðŸ¤”

venom@venom:~$ ssh -p 2220 bandit0@bandit.labs.overthewire.org
then it will ask for password put there = bandit0

In the bandit0 server there is file called readme. So to see the contents in the file we will just use CAT command
bandit0@bandit:~$ cat readme
 
then in the next line a flag will appear ðŸ™‚
Congratulations!!ðŸ¤ª that flag is the password for next level ðŸ˜Ž

FLAG will be of random characters don't worry ðŸ™‚ just copy...

Commands:-
1) SSH : (SSH client) is a program for logging into a remote machine and for executing commands on a remote machine.
         
venom@venom:~$ ssh -p 2220 bandit0@bandit.labs.overthewire.org
          
2) CAT : concatenate files and print on the standard output

bandit0@bandit:~$ cat readme

note: To exit from the connected server type exit and hit enter
